{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782440260899,"sessionID":"ses_0fe4831ceffeOChODcUYsOMwFi","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_Bhix5vuZnj9drOfjfHrD9TfJ","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\current-agent-input.md"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\current-agent-input.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Agent Input Brief - phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations / phase\n2: \n3: This brief is a narrow planning input compiled from current workflow reports. It is not an authority file.\n4: Start here, then open only the referenced source paths, target endpoints, capabilities, or reports needed for the task.\n5: \n6: ## Boundaries\n7: \n8: - Source project: `D:\\Kotlin2Cangjie\\Foodike`\n9: - Target project: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n10: - Translation inputs: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs`\n11: - Do not read sibling old translations unless the user explicitly asks for comparison.\n12: - Edit only target project files and agent-maintained authority files required by the current session.\n13: \n14: ## Freshness\n15: \n16: | artifact | exists | generatedAt | phase | error |\n17: | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n18: | phaseTaskChecklist | yes | 2026-06-26T02:17:28+00:00 | phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations |  |\n19: | phaseGroupVerdicts | yes | 2026-06-25T19:18:04+00:00 | phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations |  |\n20: | phaseCapabilityChecklist | yes | 2026-06-26T02:17:29+00:00 | phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations |  |\n21: | translationQualitySummary | yes | 2026-06-25T16:45:34+00:00 |  |  |\n22: | phaseCoverageGate | yes | 2026-06-25T19:59:16+00:00 | phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations |  |\n23: | targetStructure | yes | 2026-06-26T02:17:28+00:00 |  |  |\n24: | sourceCoverageMatrix | yes | 2026-06-25T02:01:25+00:00 |  |  |\n25: | platformCapabilityCheck | yes | 2026-06-25T02:01:25+00:00 |  |  |\n26: \n27: ## Scope Rules\n28: \n29: - Treat the current implementation group contract as the primary task input.\n30: - Open the listed source paths and target endpoints before consulting broad phase reports.\n31: - Use full phase reports as indexed references; do not sweep unrelated groups unless this group requires a small shared foundation.\n32: - Update authoritative matrix/capability rows only for this group and any directly required shared surface.\n33: \n34: ## Working Set\n35: \n36: - clusters: _none_\n37: - repair child groups: _none_\n38: - implementation groups: `phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations-source-behavior-presentation-cart`, `phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations-source-behavior-presentation-details`, `phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations-verification-phase-tests-and-evidence`\n39: - features: `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-eaf4711dc9-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-4c136b2d3d-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-f1f520ab22-005-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-8c15fff266-003-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-9969033ff2-004-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-9cef776f25-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-33250392eb-001-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-3db8c1ab5c-002-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-44d26d6a93-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-87f4a4c93e-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-93e7dc2f4a-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-3d782ce4b4-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-bb9805ee68-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-453ddde6ba-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-42a65301ac-001-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-fa0cd53e26-002-settings-preferences-option-toggles-or-c`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-de5d1e1daf-001-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodi... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n40: - capabilities: _none_\n41: - source paths: `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/Cart.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/CartViewModel.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/components/DeliverySection.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/components/ItemSection.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/components/CouponBar.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/components/BillSection.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/RestaurantDetail.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/components/MenuItemCard.kt`, `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/components/RestaurantDetailCard.kt`\n42: - target endpoints: _none_\n43: - acceptance evidence: Closed critical/high features must record sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence.; Build pass alone is not per-feature verification.; Update source-coverage-matrix.json after implementation with targetEndpoints, tests, parityLevel, and verificationEvid